            "answer_text": "Let\u2019s suppose it\u2019s true for n = k. Let\u2019s prove it for n = k + 1. S(k + 1) = S(k) + 2 * 3^k = 3^k - 1 + 2 * 3^k = 3^(k + 1) - 1 - step of induction proved. All we have to do is to check, that it\u2019s true for n = 1. Q.E.D. ",
